- **Second Layer:**

  - 2 green cubes placed on top of the yellow block.

- **Third Layer:**

  - 1 blue cube on top of the green rectangular block.

- **Top Layer:**

  - 1 yellow cylindrical block.

- **Middle Layer:**
  - 1 green rectangular block vertically placed on the yellow cylinder.

- **Top Layer:**
  - 1 orange cylindrical block horizontally placed on top of the green block.
